While Ishii-san was throttling the poor attendant, my wife and I gathered sightings from the general public. However, by the end of the event, we had not found anything useful.[l][r]
[r]Ishii-san and I were getting fed up. After putting Chito through that, he ran away without even apologizing or even giving his name. That's not what a foster parent would do.
[_tb_end_text]

