I work for a research company. I also have connections with a credit agency. Ishii-san said he would put all of his bonuses for several years into the investigation. [l][r]
And after doing our best to investigate... we found nothing.[l][r]
The results came back too quickly.
So, Ishii-san's bonus wasn't wiped out, but of course it wasn't a satisfactory result. [l][r]
However, the fact that the investigations that could be carried out at the private level were completely fruitless means that the other party was at a higher level, that is, at the national level. There was no way around it.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

